name: Stelios Hadjiperis
fullText:
@Rainmaker1973 Rumor has it Michael Jackson first came up with the anti-gravity lean after visiting this church in Ropoto, Greece back in the 80s.
Locals say he just tried to stand up straight… and “Smooth Criminal” was born. 😂
